name: LMEOW
description: LMEOW ($LMEOW) is a community-driven memecoin launched on the Solana blockchain. It operates as a fully decentralized, narrative-focused asset designed to be the definitive "Alpha Feline" token, challenging the current market dominance of dog-themed cryptocurrencies. The project is built around the cultural narrative of the GCR Prophecy, which foretells the rise of a cat-themed memecoin to achieve market supremacy. LMEOW leverages Solana's high throughput, low latency, and low transaction fees to facilitate rapid community growth and trading activity.
